product: One-Step Cloning and Chromosomal Integration of DNA
origin_organism: The flippase gene was amplified from pCP20 (e.g. available from the Coli Genetic Stock Center)
description: Can be used to remove the integration module (including the antibiotic resistance cassette) from pOSIP integrants.
shipped as: Purified Plasmid DNA, Stained with Cresol Red
growth_conditions: For propagation, please grow this plasmid in the original strain (E811) In that strain, the strong promoter pE will be repressed, thus avoiding possible toxicity and accumulation of unwanted mutations in the plasmid. Use 50ug/ml ampicillin (100ug/ml may inhibit growth)
citations: One-step cloning and chromosomal integration of DNA. St-Pierre F, Cui L, Priest DG, Endy D, Dodd IB, Shearwin KE. ACS Synth Biol. 2013 Sep 20;2(9):537-41. doi: 10.1021/sb400021j. Epub 2013 May 20. 10.1021/sb400021j PubMed 24050148
canary_notice: we are unaware of any 3rd party property rights on the use of this item
